public class Microsoft.VisualStudio.PlatformUI.AbstractPoint : ValueType {
    private Orientation _naturalOrientation;
    private Orientation _actualOrientation;
    private Point _abstractPoint;
    public Orientation NaturalOrientation { get; }
    public Orientation ActualOrientation { get; }
    public bool IsNatural { get; }
    public double AbstractX { get; public set; }
    public double AbstractY { get; public set; }
    public Point RealPoint { get; public set; }
    public double RealX { get; public set; }
    public double RealY { get; public set; }
    public AbstractPoint(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation);
    public AbstractPoint(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation, Point realPoint);
    public AbstractPoint(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation, double realX, double realY);
    public Orientation get_NaturalOrientation();
    public Orientation get_ActualOrientation();
    public bool get_IsNatural();
    public double get_AbstractX();
    public void set_AbstractX(double value);
    public double get_AbstractY();
    public void set_AbstractY(double value);
    public Point get_RealPoint();
    public void set_RealPoint(Point value);
    public double get_RealX();
    public void set_RealX(double value);
    public double get_RealY();
    public void set_RealY(double value);
    public virtual string ToString();
    public static Point Invert(Point point);
}
public class Microsoft.VisualStudio.PlatformUI.AbstractSize : ValueType {
    private Orientation _naturalOrientation;
    private Orientation _actualOrientation;
    private Size _abstractSize;
    public Orientation NaturalOrientation { get; }
    public Orientation ActualOrientation { get; }
    public bool IsNatural { get; }
    public double AbstractWidth { get; public set; }
    public double AbstractHeight { get; public set; }
    public Size RealSize { get; public set; }
    public double RealWidth { get; public set; }
    public double RealHeight { get; public set; }
    public AbstractSize(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation);
    public AbstractSize(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation, Size realSize);
    public AbstractSize(Orientation naturalOrientation, Orientation actualOrientation, double realWidth, double realHeight);
    public Orientation get_NaturalOrientation();
    public Orientation get_ActualOrientation();
    public bool get_IsNatural();
    public double get_AbstractWidth();
    public void set_AbstractWidth(double value);
    public double get_AbstractHeight();
    public void set_AbstractHeight(double value);
    public Size get_RealSize();
    public void set_RealSize(Size value);
    public double get_RealWidth();
    public void set_RealWidth(double value);
    public double get_RealHeight();
    public void set_RealHeight(double value);
    public virtual string ToString();
